My current Ether shorts are size Large and have an inseam length of 11&quot;-12&quot;. Over the years I have gone up to a Mens 38 waist, down to a 34. The sweet spot is Mens 36&quot;
I am a Carpenter and have 3 pair I have rotated for work over the past 5-6 years, wearing them 75% of the work days. These are virtually indestructible! Only one pair has retained a dime sized stain, none have fabric runs, and all the zippers work!  They are lightweight and durable and perfect for residential light construction. They might be good for mountain biking too.
Also, an iphone 13 with an otterbox fits nicely in the leg pocket of this Ether model, with easy access if you don&apos;t have thick gloves on.  I am unsure if the other Ether styles have smaller leg pocket openings depending on the inseam length.

[This review was collected as part of a promotion.] Want to maintain your modesty while feeling like you&apos;re not wearing pants at all? Colombia Silver Ridge Cargos (100% nylon ripstop material) feel, at worst, like fine Thai silk, and at best, like a cool breeze shimmering around your nether regions. Whether you&apos;re hiking, traveling, shopping, on dates, lounging at the beach, or just taking an afternoon nap, these are the best pants I&apos;ve ever stepped into. If Colombia had provided the cast of Star Trek (TNG) with outfits made of this magical stuff, we&apos;d never have heard of the &apos;Picard Maneuver.&apos;

Two deep cargo pockets on each side lay flat, so you don&apos;t need to google &apos;are cargos considered dad pants,&apos; but expand when needed for camera lenses, gadgets, or small tools, along with regular side pockets that your keys won&apos;t chew up. Everything is kept in place with an amazing belt quick-lock system that actually keeps your pants up while letting you slip through airport security with ease. If it&apos;s true that love is the reason we&apos;re here, and we should shun material things, I&apos;ve got to admit I fail—because I love these shorts. They never feel tight and are very forgiving if you happen to be a little rotund.

My very smart-looking and functional anti-cargo-cargos. Get them!
